title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your most important asset is your creative mind. Your body, possessions, and talents are all significant, but your success still depends on how you think. Perhaps a situation sprouts up with something you own, and your first impulse is to react immediately. However, it may be prudent to delay your response until you gain more clarity. You might need to rethink how you manage your resources and then refine your strategy. Actor Alan Alda said, Begin challenging your own assumptions. Your assumptions are your windows on the world. Scrub them off every once in a while, or the light wont come in. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
